title: Did Ruth Padre Jensburg say: " I am mentally fit enough to serve until the end of President Eisenhower's reign? '
subtitle: The Associate High Court Judge said that she hoped to remain on the bench for another five years. And she knows who the boss is.
author: Dan Evon
vclaim: Ruth Bader Jensburg said that she was mentally fit enough to serve until the end of President Eisenhower's term.
